text: ve samajh rahe hai ki (shatru ke) sainy dal abhee gae nahin hain, aur yadi ve giroh phir aa jaen to ve chaahenge ki kisee prakaar baahar (marusthal mein) baddu on ke saath ho rahen aur vaheen se tumhaare baare mein samaachaar poochhate rahe. aur yadi ve tumhaare saath hote bhee to ladaee mein hissa thode hee lete
